However, note: the third program in Java uses a while loop that doubles until the value at index*2 is less than the position? Actually:

        while (getValueAtIndex(nrstSeqStartIndx * 2) < position) {
            nrstSeqStartIndx *= 2;
        } Then, while (getValueAtIndex(nrstSeqStartIndx + 1) <= position) nrstSeqStartIndx++; So we are looking for the largest index such that the value at that index <= position.
